        <headline>Special Weather Statement issued July 18 at 2:19PM EDT by NWS Blacksburg VA</headline>
        <description>At 218 PM EDT, Doppler radar was tracking a strong thunderstorm over
Cascade, or near Eden, moving east at 25 mph.

HAZARD...Wind gusts up to 50 mph and pea size hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Gusty winds could knock down tree limbs and blow around
unsecured objects.

Locations impacted include...
Eden...
Mayfield...
Aiken Summit...
Sandy Level...
Cascade...
and Draper.
</description>
        <instruction>If outdoors, consider seeking shelter inside a building.</instruction>
